WEBVTT


00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:43.800
Come here.

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:45.880
Listen, Buliang.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:47.880
Today, we're only going to fight against Golden tooth.

00:01:48.080 --> 00:01:49.680
As long as you put down your weapons,

00:01:50.039 --> 00:01:52.920
I'll leave you a way out.

00:01:56.440 --> 00:01:57.240
You...

00:02:06.800 --> 00:02:09.280
Brother Shang Fei, I surrender.

00:02:09.720 --> 00:02:10.520
I surrender.

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:14.240
We can't kill each other.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.280
We've been brothers for years.

00:02:17.320 --> 00:02:18.200
Brothers?

00:02:18.600 --> 00:02:19.800
When you hurt Liang,

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:21.280
when you hurt Liang?

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:42.400
Move!

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:44.320
My brother asked me to kill this bastard.

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:45.800
You must live.

00:02:46.040 --> 00:02:48.200
You can do whatever you want to me.

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:50.000
Yes.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.760
I didn't kill Third Brother.

00:02:52.880 --> 00:02:54.240
Don't you want to know

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:55.960
who killed Third Brother?

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.480
Tell me.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:03.120
I can only tell Leader

00:03:05.880 --> 00:03:07.000
if you dare

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:09.360
If you dare to play tricks again,

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:13.360
I'll rip your skin off.

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:14.680
Guards!

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:16.760
Take him away.

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.400
Hurry!

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:24.160
Let's go.

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.560
Why isn't he here yet?

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:50.160
It shouldn't be.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:55.560
Captain Li, who are you waiting for?

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:12.440
Leader Zhu.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:16.600
What are you...

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:20.160
Tell me, did you kill Mr. Wu?

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.040
How did you know I was here?

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:23.400
Let's go.

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:25.440
Someone will tell you when we arrive.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:28.320
Where are you going?

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:01.680
You owe me

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.240
more than one life.

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:17.960
Where is my sister?

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.240
Where is Wen Pei?

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.160
You wouldn't know.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:28.880
What do you mean?

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.080
You have the jade pendant?

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:31.960
After Peking fell,

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.000
our family moved away.

00:05:33.159 --> 00:05:34.320
Didn't I go to see you?

00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:45.159
The Cui family

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:48.720
is harming others and yourself.

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:52.560
When I get rid of the Japanese,

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:55.840
I'll get even with your father.

00:05:57.560 --> 00:05:58.720
and get even with my father.

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.440
Bao.

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:10.680
My father is gone too.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:16.520
and I lost my sister.

00:06:22.320 --> 00:06:24.440
I'm just like you now.

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:26.760
He's lucky.

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.320
Take it out on me.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:33.240
After I beat the Japanese away,

00:06:33.320 --> 00:06:34.560
I'll pay with my life.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:36.200
Your father deserved it.

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:39.720
What did you say?

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:42.040
I said I didn't kill your father.

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:43.680
He deserves it.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.280
Say one more word.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:47.760
Don't move.

00:06:47.960 --> 00:06:49.680
Get out! Who let you in?

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:05.800
Don't move.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.640
Who let you two in?

00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:18.720
Do I need your help?

00:07:19.320 --> 00:07:20.560
Go out and close the door.

00:07:20.760 --> 00:07:21.800
Even if the sky collapses,

00:07:21.960 --> 00:07:23.760
Don't come in if I don't let you in.

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:25.840
Get out.

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:39.320
Okay.

00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:41.680
You want to play?

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:44.400
I'll play with you.

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:46.800
I can see

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.760
what you've learned these years.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.000
Should we go in and take a look?

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.080
Do you want to be beaten?

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:39.760
Brigade Commander won't let us in.

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:40.640
We'd better not go in.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:58.040
You're quite skilled now.

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:02.120
You've practiced well outside these years.

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:05.200
You are a high official now.

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:08.120
The army is different from us.

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:09.360
Besides,

00:10:09.880 --> 00:10:10.960
when you were little,

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:12.600
you couldn't beat me.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:13.680
Nonsense.

00:10:14.360 --> 00:10:16.040
I always let you win when I was young.

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:17.440
Forget it.

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:19.680
My father told me in private

00:10:19.880 --> 00:10:22.320
to let you win all the time.

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:24.160
Let me tell you.

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.760
It's not that Wen Pei always misses his hand.

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:26.600
Look at you.

00:10:26.640 --> 00:10:27.840
Maybe something is missing.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.440
You're not convinced?

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:33.120
Let's continue.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:34.400
I'll give you two hands.

00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:35.560
Enough.

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:42.480
Tell me the truth.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:46.040
WenPei didn't come to you, right?

00:10:50.640 --> 00:10:51.560
At that time,

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:55.080
I didn't know where to go.

00:11:00.840 --> 00:11:02.160
You know what? For so many years,

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:02.840
I really hope

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:04.680
WenPei would be with you.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:14.240
Report!

00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:16.600
Brigade Commander.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:18.040
Speak.

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:19.600
Shangguan Eagle is injured.

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:58.080
You, save him!

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:21.160
Stop!

00:12:21.320 --> 00:12:22.000
Mother!

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:24.280
What are you doing in the middle of the night?

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:25.480
There are so many men out there.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:26.760
They're all men. Let's go home.

00:12:26.960 --> 00:12:28.360
I'm just going out.

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:30.080
What are you looking at?

00:12:30.400 --> 00:12:31.120
Go back.

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:32.360
Dad, you're back.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.120
Slow down.

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:40.040
Don't fall, you crazy girl.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:12:58.840
Aunt Soo.

00:12:59.040 --> 00:12:59.920
Did you see someone?

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:01.720
Someone went that way.

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:20.280
Brother Xi!

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:24.360
Stop fighting!

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.920
Aunt Shui, I saw that man

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:28.080
He's not as tall as you.

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:29.440
He's small.

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:31.080
Little one.

00:13:31.080 --> 00:13:31.960
What's wrong, Ni?

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:34.680
Jintooth is dead.

00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:35.800
The golden tooth is dead.

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:37.040
Isn't the wooden prison guarded?

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:38.480
They're all dead.

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:41.080
Fly on the boat.

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:42.960
What are you doing here?

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:44.840
Madam asked me to patrol.

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:46.720
Don’t ask me. Go to the wood dungeon.

00:13:50.560 --> 00:13:51.520
Wait for me!

00:14:06.560 --> 00:14:07.760
Who killed him?

00:14:14.200 --> 00:14:15.160
Kill him to silence him.

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:18.680
He must know something.

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:20.320
The knife is fast.

00:14:20.520 --> 00:14:22.080
It doesn't look like our knife.

00:14:22.600 --> 00:14:23.800
It looks like a Japanese knife.

00:14:25.600 --> 00:14:26.600
Seal down the fortress.

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:28.040
No one is allowed to go out.

00:14:28.320 --> 00:14:29.280
No.

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:33.200
I'm sure it wasn't

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:35.560
must not be done by an ordinary brother.

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:36.480
If that's the case,

00:14:36.680 --> 00:14:38.880
the murderer should have a high status.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:44.640
Did the Japanese order Big Jaws to do it?

00:14:50.040 --> 00:14:50.880
Nini.

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:53.040
Didn't you see someone?

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:54.760
Yes.

00:14:55.560 --> 00:14:57.960
I saw someone.

00:14:58.480 --> 00:14:59.400
See clearly.

00:15:00.760 --> 00:15:01.480
No.

00:15:01.840 --> 00:15:02.960
It's too dark.

00:15:03.880 --> 00:15:06.000
I just thought he was sneaky

00:15:06.160 --> 00:15:06.840
so I followed him.

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.400
In the end,

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:11.840
Say it.

00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:13.960
Then I saw

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:14.880
with Aunt Shui.

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:19.960
Fly on the boat.

00:15:20.560 --> 00:15:21.800
Why are you there?

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:22.800
All right.

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:26.240
Tomorrow morning, all our men will go back to their fortress.

00:15:26.840 --> 00:15:28.640
You go to Black Tiger Mountain to be the head.

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:29.880
Madam.

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.640
What about Qingfeng Camp?

00:15:31.880 --> 00:15:33.680
Leave Qingfeng Camp to the Second Master.

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:36.760
You’re in charge of these two villages.

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:37.440
But he...

00:15:37.520 --> 00:15:38.360
Liu.

00:15:39.160 --> 00:15:41.680
Trust me that I'll find out the truth.

00:15:53.480 --> 00:15:54.240
Alright.

00:15:54.440 --> 00:15:55.680
She should be fine.

00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:57.000
If it doesn’t work,

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:58.280
I'll explain

00:15:58.600 --> 00:15:59.680
to Qinglong Fortress.

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:02.680
It's all my fault.

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:05.480
I was too naive.

00:16:06.840 --> 00:16:08.280
If I had gone,

00:16:09.680 --> 00:16:11.480
this wouldn’t have happened.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:14.600
The letter from the Patriarch of Qinglong Fortress.

00:16:15.240 --> 00:16:16.280
Do you want to take a look?

00:16:28.600 --> 00:16:29.520
The golden knife seal.

00:16:30.400 --> 00:16:31.320
belongs to my father.

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:34.520
How have you been, Brigade Commander Cui?

00:16:34.640 --> 00:16:35.520
You've been changing lately.

00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:38.120
Among the swordsmen,

00:16:38.400 --> 00:16:42.000
I also found something to bully the people.

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:44.960
His behavior is very domineering and weird.

00:16:45.200 --> 00:16:47.800
He must have colluded with

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:49.080
and Japanese.

00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:51.000
So it's decided tonight.

00:16:51.360 --> 00:16:53.040
I will lead the army to attack.

00:16:53.320 --> 00:16:54.400
I've thought about it.

00:16:54.560 --> 00:16:56.160
I'm worried that there might be foreign aid.

00:16:56.280 --> 00:16:58.760
Please cooperate with us.

00:16:59.240 --> 00:17:00.200
Shangguan Bao.

00:17:01.200 --> 00:17:02.160
Are you sure?

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.160
What's your plan after reading the letter?

00:17:15.680 --> 00:17:17.280
Someone said that the swordsman hijacked the refugees

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:19.520
to ruin the reputation of the swordsman.

00:17:19.520 --> 00:17:22.160
and forced me to go against the swordsman.

00:17:23.599 --> 00:17:25.480
Golden tooth, it must be him.

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:34.000
But if it was Li Gang

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:35.200
is Li Gang,

00:17:35.800 --> 00:17:36.800
At this time,

00:17:37.120 --> 00:17:40.160
he should pretend to be his enemy.

00:17:41.240 --> 00:17:42.640
That's a cruel move.

00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:44.200
Poison?

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:45.880
What do you mean?

00:17:46.320 --> 00:17:48.200
Li Gang will lead the bandits

00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:50.800
they will immediately get the support of the refugees without knowing it.

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:51.680
And think about it.

00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:52.600
If the Japanese

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:54.280
the Japanese would attack us now.

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:55.360
What are we doing?

00:17:55.640 --> 00:17:57.280
We're on the same side.

00:17:57.640 --> 00:17:59.960
they can only take advantage of it.

00:18:02.800 --> 00:18:03.760
I see.

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:06.080
If you don't hit the swordsman, the refugees won't agree.

00:18:06.280 --> 00:18:07.400
If you hit the swordsman,

00:18:07.560 --> 00:18:08.840
the local people won't agree.

00:18:09.040 --> 00:18:10.000
Right?

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:11.040
Yes.

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:14.640
You can't leave here either.

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:17.040
Why?

00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:20.200
I think someone will be watching you.

00:18:20.440 --> 00:18:22.760
If you leave here, you'll alert them.

00:18:24.120 --> 00:18:25.440
Japanese?

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:27.120
Not only Japanese.

00:18:27.320 --> 00:18:29.720
I'm afraid there are many people in the army.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:32.800
Are you implying something?

00:18:35.200 --> 00:18:36.880
The adjutant beside you.

00:18:37.040 --> 00:18:39.040
What do you think? Surprised?

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:52.360
Those bastards.

00:18:53.560 --> 00:18:56.200
All you do is keep an eye on your own people.

00:18:58.280 --> 00:18:59.080
Eagle.

00:18:59.360 --> 00:19:00.760
Go back to the fortress now.

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:02.160
and tell Madam

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:03.680
the situation here.

00:19:03.880 --> 00:19:05.120
This is the best choice.

00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:15.720
Doctor, how is she?

00:19:16.080 --> 00:19:17.400
The bullet has been removed.

00:19:17.560 --> 00:19:18.560
She's not in danger.

00:19:18.760 --> 00:19:20.680
She needs some rest to wake up.

00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:22.000
Thank you.

00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:22.880
You're welcome.

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:33.760
Miss, you're awake.

00:19:44.040 --> 00:19:45.040
Where am I?

00:19:51.680 --> 00:19:53.080
Miss, don't move.

00:19:53.360 --> 00:19:55.200
Miss, you can't move.

00:19:55.520 --> 00:19:57.120
You have a wound here. Don't move.

00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:57.920
Where am I?

00:19:58.000 --> 00:19:58.800
This is a hospital.

00:19:58.920 --> 00:20:00.920
Lie down. You have a wound.

00:20:01.040 --> 00:20:02.360
Come on, lie down. I want to go out.

00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:04.160
I want to go out.

00:20:04.280 --> 00:20:05.360
Miss, where are you going? I want to go out.

00:20:05.480 --> 00:20:06.680
Don't move, miss.

00:20:07.400 --> 00:20:08.560
Miss, where are you going?

00:20:08.800 --> 00:20:10.160
You can't move. Lie down.

00:20:10.240 --> 00:20:11.240
I want to go out. Don't move.

00:20:11.240 --> 00:20:12.320
Don't move. Eagle, who are you?

00:20:12.440 --> 00:20:14.320
Eagle, I'm here.

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:16.600
This is the hospital. Don't pull it out. This is medicine.

00:20:16.800 --> 00:20:17.840
It can cure you.

00:20:18.080 --> 00:20:20.120
I thought I would never see you again.

00:20:20.680 --> 00:20:22.680
I thought I would die like this.

00:20:22.840 --> 00:20:24.280
You didn't. Don't be afraid.

00:20:24.480 --> 00:20:25.440
I'm here.

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:29.400
Don't be afraid.

00:20:31.480 --> 00:20:32.560
Don't think about anything now.

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:35.400
Just recuperate.

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:38.400
Don't cry.

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:46.920
Don't cry.

00:20:47.680 --> 00:20:48.640
I'm here.

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:06.440
Take off all the iron on you.

00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:10.840
What?

00:21:12.120 --> 00:21:12.960
I dare not.

00:21:59.240 --> 00:22:02.000
Why did you go to the backyard at that time?

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:03.240
I always suspect

00:22:03.440 --> 00:22:05.080
someone sent news to the outside.

00:22:05.360 --> 00:22:07.160
So I go there every day.

00:22:07.320 --> 00:22:08.320
Did you find anything?

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:09.800
Nothing.

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:11.600
How many years have you been on the mountain?

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:13.280
Three months and six years.

00:22:13.480 --> 00:22:14.560
I remember it clearly.

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:17.320
Without a purpose,

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.840
who would remember

00:22:20.040 --> 00:22:21.280
for a few years?

00:22:30.360 --> 00:22:31.600
Who are you?

00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:40.800
It's true that I work for the army.

00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:42.560
But for so many years,

00:22:42.840 --> 00:22:45.040
I've never done anything

00:22:45.040 --> 00:22:46.200
to you.

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:49.080
nor did I do anything to Qinglong Fortress.

00:23:18.240 --> 00:23:19.120
How is she?

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:22.600
She's asleep.

00:23:22.800 --> 00:23:24.240
Apart from being a little stubborn,

00:23:26.040 --> 00:23:27.080
she's actually not bad.

00:23:30.280 --> 00:23:31.920
I don't have that many tricks.

00:23:34.520 --> 00:23:35.880
Can you control them?

00:23:39.360 --> 00:23:40.720
We're fake.

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:49.360
I just saw

00:23:51.640 --> 00:23:52.960
it doesn't look fake.

00:23:58.320 --> 00:23:59.160
What about you?

00:23:59.400 --> 00:24:00.320
What?

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:02.040
Are you married?

